<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10086585>
    dc:description "FIGURE 40. Upper (A), Lower (B), and Lateral (C) views of a mature nectophore of Halistemma striata. For Legend see Figures 14 and 29. Scale bar 5mm." ;
