    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10086593>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Halistemma striata. Thickened tentacle bearing tentilla on long pedicels. Scale bar 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10086593/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10086595>
    dc:description "FIGURE 45. Halistemma striata. Individual tentillum (scale bar 5 mm), with (inset) detail of terminal filament (scale bar 2 mm.) i indicates the distal most tip of the involucrum." ;
