    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10086597>
    dc:description "FIGURE 47. Halistemma striata. Part of partially denuded siphosome (anterior to the right). fg: female gonodendron, with gonophores borne on a broad thin stalk (sfg); mg: male gonodendra 1, 2, 3 and 4; p: palpon. Scale bar 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10086597/files/figure.png" ;
